pageContext.claim: “A woman I don't know and, to the best of my knowledge, never met, is on the FRONT PAGE of the Fake News Washington Post saying I kissed her (for two minutes yet) in the lobby of Trump Tower 12 years ago. Never happened! Who would do this in a public space with live security cameras running.”
pageContext.analysis: Rachel Crooks said the encounter did not take place in a public space but near the elevators on the 24th floor of the Trump Tower.
